name: JWSDL
short_description: JWSDL is a light weight WSDL parsing java API. By parsing WSDL file, it can return a JTree Object or output each method which is defined in wsdl to console. Comparing other API, JWSDL can recursively parse n-Tier arrays which defined in WSDL.
